{% extends "layouts/default.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="container">
    {% include "layouts/partials/header.njk" %}

    {% import "layouts/macros/nav-macro.njk" as nav %}
    {{nav.active('')}}

    <section class="section__container">
      <h1 class="project__title">Glassbreakers</h1>
      <h2 class="project__subtitle">UX/UI</h2>
      <section class="project__info">
        <div class="project__info-module">
          <div class="project__info-title">Expertise</div>
          <ul class="project__info-list">
            <li class="project__info-item">UX/UI Design</li>
            <li class="project__info-item">Design/Tech Documentation</li>
            <li class="project__info-item">Front-end Implementation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="project__info-module">
          <div class="project__info-title">Links</div>
          <ul class="project__info-list">
            <li class="project__info-item"><a class="project__link" href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/jeffreyqua/gb_brand.pdf">Brand and tone guide</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <figure class="project__image-container">
        <img src="images/projects/gb-messaging.jpg" class="project__image" alt="GB Messaging" />
        <figcaption class="project__image-caption">GB Messaging</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <section class="project__block">
        <h3 class="project__block-title">Objective</h3>
        <p>The Glassbreakers product team needed to coordinate product and design decisions to the engineering team. Any feature and update required UI mockups and technical notes to outline intended functionality.</p>
      </section>

      <figure class="project__image-container">
        <img src="images/projects/gb-profile.jpg" class="project__image" alt="GB Profile" />
        <figcaption class="project__image-caption">GB Profile</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <section class="project__block">
        <h3 class="project__block-title">Approach</h3>
        <p>In order to communicate design rationale on features, I had to create technical and design documentation to explain specific technical implementation and usability requirements.</p>
      </section>

      <figure class="project__image-container">
        <img src="images/projects/gb-uxflow.jpg" class="project__image" alt="Sample UX Flowchart" />
        <figcaption class="project__image-caption">Sample UX Flowchart</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <section class="project__block">
        <h3 class="project__block-title">Process</h3>
        <p>All features were documented with screenshots of all possible states and documented in our company wiki.</p>

        <p>Our team's TDD approach influenced our design methodology as well by incorporating view spec tests, and also testing email fidelity with Litmus.</p>
      </section>

      <figure class="project__image-container">
        <img src="images/projects/gb-metrics.jpg" class="project__image" alt="GB Metrics" />
        <figcaption class="project__image-caption">GB Metrics Dashboard</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <section class="project-nav">
        <div class="project-nav__prev">
          <a href="gb-brand.html" class="project-nav__link">&lt; Previous Project</a>
        </div>
        <div class="project-nav__next">
          <a href="centerpoint.html" class="project-nav__link">Next Project &gt;</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>

  </div>
  {% include "layouts/partials/footer.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
